title: Tangará, Rio Grande do Norte
text: Tangará is a <a href="Municipalities%20of%20Brazil">municipality</a> in the <a href="states%20of%20Brazil">state</a> of <a href="Rio%20Grande%20do%20Norte">Rio Grande do Norte</a> in the <a href="Northeast%20Region%2C%20Brazil">Northeast region</a> of <a href="Brazil">Brazil</a>.
